
<p>
  Tv show data last updated on: {{updateHistory}}
</p>

<p>
  {{#if isRecentlyUpdated}}
    Show data was recently updated
  {{else}}
    Show data was not recently updated
  {{/if}}
</p>

<p>
  Everytime you visit the homepage active shows might be updated with new data if it has been 3 days since it was last updated.
</p>

<p>
  If you would like to force show data to be updated you can click this button.
</p>
<form action="/admin/update_show_data" onsubmit="this.querySelector('button').disabled = true">
  <input type="hidden" name="force" value="true" />
  <button>get new data</button>
</form>

